text: I'm a Celebrity... South Africa is an ITV reality television series, with the premise being an All Star edition of I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! featuring campmates from previous series. The series aired between 24 April and 12 May 2023. Ant & Dec presented the series. On 12 May 2023, series 6 runner-up Myleene Klasswas crowned winner of the series after defeating series 16 campmate Jordan Banjo in the final survival trial, who ultimately finished as runner-up.
